						 <p>i love this scp. there are many questions about where the foundation gets its resources; how do they afford it? how do they power everything? etc.</p> <p>this scp answers that question pretty succinctly by saying &quot;the SCP Foundation is powered by funny cat pictures, deal with it.&quot;</p> <p>+1</p> 
				 	]]>
