				<pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2020 20:15:55 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>cybersqyd</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5336470</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm not going to implement your ending here because it'd feel emotionally abrupt and it'd raise questions about e.g, why the Foundation running these generators at a comparatively small scale internally would affect the world. I considered making it a running theme throughout, and using Ethics Committee interviews to highlight it but ultimately, I decided it'd detract from the narrative by adding an additional narrative layer on top of what's already here.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
