					<![CDATA[
						 <p>upvoted after much hesitation, but take your victories where you get 'em.</p> <p>Consider switching the end to &quot;the fundation is powering their sites and experiments via love, as such love worldwide is being reduced and it causes a few civil wars and such.&quot;</p> <p>According to a projection, all love will be consumed in 2029 to keep SCP-[blackblackblackblack] in check as no other power source can suffice.</p> <p>ALTERNATIVELY: provide many sample kitten pictures and you shall be forgiven.</p> 
